## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Core Shared Kernel

Move cross-cutting concerns out of `main.py` into a proper `core/` shared kernel.

---

#### [MODIFY] [core/](file:///home/adesh-yadav/Desktop/content_tool/app/core) вҖ” Shared Kernel Restructure

```
app/core/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”ңв”Җв”Җ domain/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ aggregate_root.py          # [NEW] Base AggregateRoot with domain events
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_entity.py             # [MOVE] from core/entities/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ value_objects.py           # [MOVE] from core/entities/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ domain_event.py            # [NEW] Base DomainEvent class
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ domain_service.py          # [NEW] Base DomainService ABC
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ application/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_use_case.py           # [MOVE] from core/interfaces/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_command.py            # [NEW] CQRS Command base
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_query.py              # [NEW] CQRS Query base
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ unit_of_work.py            # [NEW] UoW interface for transactions
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ port/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ input/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ __init__.py            # Marker вҖ” feature ports go inside features
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ output/
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ repository_port.py     # [MOVE+RENAME] from core/interfaces/base_repository.py
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ llm_port.py            # [MOVE+RENAME] from core/interfaces/llm_provider.py
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ event_publisher_port.py # [NEW] Domain event publishing port
в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ cache_port.py          # [NEW] Caching port
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ exception/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_exception.py          # [MOVE+SPLIT] DomainException from exceptions.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ not_found.py               # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ validation_error.py        # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ authentication_error.py    # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ authorization_error.py     # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ quota_exceeded.py          # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ llm_provider_error.py      # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ duplicate_error.py         # [MOVE+SPLIT]
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ exception_handler/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ fastapi_handlers.py        # [NEW] Extracted from main.py
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ middleware/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ cors.py                    # [NEW] Extracted CORS setup
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ request_logging.py         # [NEW] Extracted request logging
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ request_id.py              # [NEW] X-Request-ID middleware
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ response/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ api_response.py            # [MOVE] from core/response.py
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ router/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ registry.py                # [NEW] Centralized router registration
в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җ utils/
    в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
    в””в”Җв”Җ logger.py                  # [KEEP]
```

**Key changes:**
- `AggregateRoot` extends `BaseEntity` with `_domain_events: list[DomainEvent]` for event collection
- Each exception gets its own file (SRP)
- Exception handlers, middleware, router registration extracted from `main.py`
- CQRS base classes (`BaseCommand`, `BaseQuery`) for input DTOs
- `UnitOfWork` interface for transactional consistency

---

### Phase 2: Multi-LLM Provider System

---

#### [MODIFY] [infrastructure/ai/](file:///home/adesh-yadav/Desktop/content_tool/app/infrastructure/ai) вҖ” Multi-Provider LLM

```
app/infrastructure/ai/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”ңв”Җв”Җ llm_registry.py                # [NEW] Registry of all available providers
в”ңв”Җв”Җ llm_factory.py                 # [REFACTOR] Factory with provider registry
в”ңв”Җв”Җ providers/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ openai_provider.py         # [MOVE+SPLIT] from llm_factory.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ anthropic_provider.py      # [MOVE+SPLIT] from llm_factory.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ google_provider.py         # [NEW] Google Gemini via langchain-google-genai
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ huggingface_provider.py    # [NEW] HuggingFace via langchain-huggingface
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ollama_provider.py         # [NEW] Ollama local models via langchain-ollama
в””в”Җв”Җ model_config.py                # [NEW] Per-feature model recommendations
```

**LLM Registry** design вҖ” allows per-feature LLM selection:

```python
# Example: feature can request a specific provider
llm = llm_registry.get_provider("google", model="gemini-2.0-flash")
llm = llm_registry.get_provider("ollama", model="llama3")
llm = llm_registry.get_provider("huggingface", model="mistralai/Mistral-7B")
```

**Config additions** (`.env`):
```env
LLM_PROVIDER=openai                    # default provider
GOOGLE_API_KEY=...
GOOGLE_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash
HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY=...
HUGGINGFACE_MODEL=mistralai/Mistral-7B
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3
```

**`model_config.py`** вҖ” per-feature LLM recommendations:
```python
FEATURE_LLM_MAP = {
    "blog_generator":       {"provider": "openai",    "model": "gpt-4o"},
    "article_writer":       {"provider": "anthropic",  "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet"},
    "social_media":         {"provider": "openai",    "model": "gpt-4o-mini"},
    "ad_copy":              {"provider": "openai",    "model": "gpt-4o-mini"},
    "product_description":  {"provider": "openai",    "model": "gpt-4o-mini"},
    "email_writer":         {"provider": "anthropic",  "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet"},
    "script_writer":        {"provider": "openai",    "model": "gpt-4o"},
    "seo_optimizer":        {"provider": "google",    "model": "gemini-2.0-flash"},
}
```

Each feature's AI adapter can override the default via config or per-request.

---

### Phase 3: Feature Refactoring (Hexagonal + DDD)

Below is the **target structure for EVERY feature**. I show the full tree for `auth` and `blog_generator` as reference, then list file names for all other features.

