### Phase 5: Refactored `main.py` and `dependencies.py`

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///home/adesh-yadav/Desktop/content_tool/app/main.py)

Becomes minimal вҖ” delegates to core modules:

```python
# main.py (target вҖ” ~30 lines)
from app.core.middleware.cors import setup_cors
from app.core.middleware.request_logging import setup_request_logging
from app.core.exception_handler.fastapi_handlers import register_exception_handlers
from app.core.router.registry import register_all_routers

def create_app() -> FastAPI:
    app = FastAPI(...)
    setup_cors(app)
    setup_request_logging(app)
    register_exception_handlers(app)
    register_all_routers(app)
    return app
```

#### [MODIFY] [dependencies.py](file:///home/adesh-yadav/Desktop/content_tool/app/dependencies.py)

Add multi-LLM dependency:

```python
def get_llm(provider: str | None = None, model: str | None = None) -> ILLMProvider:
    return llm_registry.get_provider(provider, model)
```

