> [!IMPORTANT]
> 2. **LLM providers**: Which providers do you definitely want included? (OpenAI вң…, Anthropic вң…, Google Gemini, HuggingFace, Ollama вҖ” all?)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 3. **Database migration**: Should I create Alembic migrations for any new models, or handle that separately?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 4. **Per-request LLM**: Should users be able to pass `llm_provider` in the API request body to override the default per-feature LLM?

